flowchart TD
    Start([Upload or ingest_samples.py]) --> Parse{File extension}

    Parse -->|.pdf| PDF[PyMuPDF extract_text]
    Parse -->|.docx| DOCX[python-docx paragraphs]
    Parse -->|.txt .md| TXT[UTF-8 read]
    Parse -->|other| Fail[status FAILED]

    PDF --> Chunk
    DOCX --> Chunk
    TXT --> Chunk

    Chunk[build_chunks_with_metadata<br/>size 1000 overlap 100<br/>section + line metadata]
    Chunk --> Embed[SentenceTransformer<br/>all-MiniLM-L6-v2]
    Embed --> WriteChroma[ChromaDB documents_v1<br/>cosine HNSW]
    Embed --> WriteSQL[SQLite chunks table<br/>id document_id section]
    WriteChroma --> Indexed[Document status INDEXED]
    WriteSQL --> Indexed

    subgraph AccessLevels["Sample doc access levels"]
        A1[employee_handbook PUBLIC 1]
        A2[hanuinnotech_* PUBLIC 1]
        A3[product_spec_v3 INTERNAL 2]
        A4[board_meeting_june RESTRICTED 4]
        A5[other samples INTERNAL 2]
    end
